oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Alma Hastings and Sue Wells in the kitchen of the Hastings home
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Black and white photograph of the interior of the Hastings home. Alma Hastings and Sue Wells, a TVA home economist, are shown in the kitchen.
The Hasting's home had just had electricity installed when the photograph was taken.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Looking Back at Tennessee Photograph Collection, 1890-1981
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Home economics; Kitchens; Stoves; Cookery; Interiors
